## 📝 WORKFLOW

### Complete Security Flow

```
1. Client requests stream access:
   GET /watch?userId=USER&camera=CAMERA

2. Backend validates:
   ✓ User exists and is active
   ✓ Camera exists and is active
   ✓ User-Camera link exists
   ✓ Access rules allow (day/time)

3. If valid, generate JWT:
   ✓ Contains: sub (userId), camera (name)
   ✓ Expires: 60 seconds
   ✓ Signed with secret key

4. Return stream URL with token:
   http://localhost:8888/CAMERA?token=JWT

5. Client accesses stream:
   GET http://localhost:8888/CAMERA?token=JWT

6. MediaMTX intercepts and validates:
   POST /api/access/stream/validate?token=JWT&stream=CAMERA

7. Backend validates JWT:
   ✓ Check signature (secret key)
   ✓ Check expiration (< 60s)
   ✓ Extract claims (userId, camera)
   ✓ Verify user exists and active
   ✓ Verify camera exists and active
   ✓ Verify user-camera link
   ✓ Verify access rules (day/time)

8. Respond:
   ✓ 200 OK → MediaMTX allows access
   ✓ 401 Unauthorized → MediaMTX blocks access

9. Log audit entry:
   INSERT INTO access_logs (user_id, camera_id, allowed, reason, source)
```

---

## 🚀 Quick Test Script

```bash
#!/bin/bash

# 1. Get token
echo "📋 Step 1: Getting token..."
RESPONSE=$(curl -s "http://localhost:5001/watch?userId=test-user&camera=test")
STREAM_URL=$(echo $RESPONSE | jq -r '.streamUrl')
TOKEN=$(echo $STREAM_URL | sed 's/.*token=//')

echo "✅ Token obtained: $TOKEN"
echo "   Stream URL: $STREAM_URL"

# 2. Validate token directly
echo ""
echo "📋 Step 2: Validating token..."
curl -s "http://localhost:5001/api/access/stream/validate?token=$TOKEN&stream=test&ip=127.0.0.1" | jq

# 3. Try expired token
echo ""
echo "📋 Step 3: Waiting 65 seconds for token to expire..."
sleep 65

echo ""
echo "📋 Step 4: Validating expired token (should fail)..."
curl -s "http://localhost:5001/api/access/stream/validate?token=$TOKEN&stream=test&ip=127.0.0.1" | jq

echo ""
echo "✅ Test completed!"
```

---

## 🔒 Security Validation Checklist

- [ ] Token obtained successfully
- [ ] Token validated successfully  
- [ ] Stream accessible with valid token
- [ ] Token expires after 60 seconds
- [ ] Expired token blocks access
- [ ] Tampered token blocks access
- [ ] Token without secret fails
- [ ] Wrong stream name fails
- [ ] Logs record all attempts
- [ ] 200 OK allows, 401 blocks
- [ ] No direct access possible
- [ ] All claims verified

